        "content": "<p>myunbin opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12978\">PR #12978</a> from <code>myunbin:add-rules-040726</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This PR adds several simplification rules:</p>\n<p><code>arithmetic.isle</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>min/max(x,x) --&gt; x</code></li>\n<li><code>max(max(x, y), x) --&gt; max(x, y)</code></li>\n<li><code>min(min(x, y), x) --&gt; min(x, y)</code></li>\n<li><code>min(max(x, y), y) --&gt; y ; max(min(x, y), y) --&gt; y</code></li>\n<li><code>min(min(x, y), max(x, y)) --&gt; min(x,y)</code></li>\n<li><code>max(min(x, y), max(x, y)) --&gt; max(x, y)</code></li>\n<li><code>x &gt; max(x, y) --&gt; 0</code></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>",
